# Cursor Rules (n8n repo-first)
#
# Source of truth:
# - Workflows are stored as JSON files in `workflows/*.json` and are versioned on a separate Git branch `workflows`.
# - Lab tooling (MCP server, schemas, docs, kb) lives on Git branch `lab`.
#
# Tooling:
# - Python environment: uv
# - Task runner: Poe the Poet (docs): https://poethepoet.natn.io/
#
# Operational rules:
# - Prefer using the local MCP server tools for all workflow CRUD/patch/validate/format and Git operations.
# - Avoid manual editing of large workflow JSON blobs unless explicitly requested by the user.
#
# Canonical reference:
# - See `agents/agents.md` for the authoritative agent policy and official n8n sources by topic.


